Some crew members are complaining about another's snoring. As minor as the problem is, you don't want your crew members losing sleep. You ask Ripley if she can do something about it. She replies, "Surely there are more pressing matters than a crew member's noisy snoring...I have some medicine that alleviates snoring as a side effect, but weâ€™ll have to restock it before someone catches a real disease. I know Lexa would disagree, but it would probably be best to just let the crew suffer through it."
+ [Treat the Snoring] -> Treat
