=== Treat ===
A well-rested crew is a happy crew. Paying a few credits so that the crew sleeps well is better than giving them all a raise to prevent a riot. You have Ripley give the problem causer some pills to take before bed that should prevent the snoring.
-> END

=== Allow ===
You decide to take Ripley's advice. Preventing a little unhappiness is not worth a loss of credits. If it's really keeping them up at night, your crew members can get ear plugs. With their own credits.
-> END

